                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040411-56-defend597 t18040411-56-punish331"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
